projects.name: LeafSnap
projects.description: Indian Leaf Disease Detection Mobile Application. Prepared Datasets of following leaves: Mango, Bay Leaf, Ladyfinger, Java Plum from local farm houses. Applied Image pre-processing techniques such as augmentation, edge detection and graysaling. Did training and testing of dataset on ML Model(CNN) to identify leaf type with an accuracy of 90.25%. Developed a Mobile application where users can scan leaves, and get the disease name.

projects.name: CoinSearch
projects.description: Cryptocurrency Screener Web Application. Built a website for displaying basic information such as Name, Symbol, Price, description, of cryptocurrencies. Used API from CoinGeckoAPI to fetch information related to particular coin.

projects.name: Gene Desktop Voice Assistant
projects.description: Windows Application. Developed a Desktop voice assistant application that helps automate basic tasks such as opening apps, setting alarm, controlling in-app buttons and searching Wikipedia by predefined using voice. Made a website for downloading the assistant and hosted it using Github Pages. Used NSIS software to convert .py to executable file.

projects.name: WeatherX
projects.description: Live Weather data Web Application. Built a responsive website with ability to search for any locations weather. Used APIs from OpenWeatherAPI and Unsplash to fetch weather information and image of location.
